creatureBayingGourmetMale.name: Baying Gourmet
creatureBayingGourmetMale.appDesc: You are covered in a thick layer of fur. Your face is that of large manacing wolf. You really look like a monster from the Abyss!

creatureBayingGourmetFemale.name: Baying Gourmet
creatureBayingGourmetFemale.appDesc: You are covered in a thick layer of fur. Your face is that of large manacing wolf. You really look like a monster from the Abyss!

creatureDragonMale.name: Dragon
creatureDragonMale.appDesc: Your scaly hide and horns combined with the reptilian wings can only mean one thing. You look like a fearsome dragon!

creatureDragonFemale.name: Dragon
creatureDragonFemale.appDesc: Your scaly hide and horns combined with the reptilian wings can only mean one thing. You look like a fearsome dragon!

companionMaru.name: Maru
companionMaru.appDesc: Your skin is extremely soft and bruises easily. Any material rougher than silk feels uncomfortable on it now.

companionLily.name: Lily
companionLily.appDesc: You have particularly long eyelashes, and your legs seem long compared to your height. Your pupils are heart-shaped.

companionKhemia.name: Khemia
companionKhemia.appDesc: You have blue spiral tattoos through the length of both arms, and your hands are calloused from over a decade of hard work. Your voice seems to draw more attention than it used to before switching bodies.

companionCherry.name: Cherry
companionCherry.appDesc: Your body feels low on energy often, and you feel like you need more sleep than you used to.

companionCloud.name: Cloud
companionCloud.appDesc: Your sight is pretty good, and you can focus on distant objects more easily. Your smile seems to easily earn people's trust.

companionSaeko.name: Saeko
companionSaeko.appDesc: Your sight is pretty bad without glasses and your eyebrows are relatively thin.

companionBandit.name: The bandit
companionBandit.appDesc: You're pretty athletic from brawling and robbing people every day.

companionAI.name: Ai
companionAI.appDesc: You're an AI, now what? At this point you're simply a virtual avatar and rely on your physical companions to help you on your journey.

companionGolem.name: Golem
companionGolem.appDesc: You are a sturdy clay golem.

companionTwin.name: Twin
companionTwin.appDesc: You basically feel the same as always.

purityPlank.name: Purity Tree Plank
purityPlank.desc: A plank of wood taken from a rare breed of tree that somehow developed a way to absorb the natural miasma of the Abyss.

relics.name: Starlit Conquest Activated
relics.desc: The starlit conquest mecha in all its glory. It has been activated by the power of the sun and is ready for use!
